14#include <memory>

16#include "absl/base/attributes.h"
17#include "modules/include/module.h"
18#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtp_rtcp_interface.h"
19
20namespace webrtc {
21
22// DEPRECATED. Do not use.
23class RtpRtcp : public Module, public RtpRtcpInterface {
24 public:
25 // Instantiates a deprecated version of the RtpRtcp module.
26 static std::unique_ptr<RtpRtcp> ABSL_DEPRECATED("")
27 Create(const Configuration& configuration) {
28 return DEPRECATED_Create(configuration);
29 }
30
31 static std::unique_ptr<RtpRtcp> DEPRECATED_Create(
32 const Configuration& configuration);
33
34 // Requests new key frame.
35 // using PLI, https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4585#section-6.3.1.1
36 void SendPictureLossIndication() { SendRTCP(kRtcpPli); }
37 // using FIR, https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5104#section-4.3.1.2
38 void SendFullIntraRequest() { SendRTCP(kRtcpFir); }
39};
40
41} // namespace webrtc

43#endif // MODULES_RTP_RTCP_INCLUDE_RTP_RTCP_H_
